## 🔍 Verifying logrotate config written to /etc/logrotate.d/myapp

> **Timestamp:** `2026-06-16 09:17:24`

### 01. `cat /etc/logrotate.d/myapp`

```bash
cat /etc/logrotate.d/myapp
```

**Output:**

```text
/var/log/myapp/*.log {
    daily
    rotate 14
    compress
    delaycompress
    missingok
    notifempty
    create 0640 root root
    sharedscripts
    postrotate
        echo "[$(date)] Log rotated by logrotate" >> /var/log/myapp/app.log
    endscript
}
```


